title: StyloPoly

content.no: StyloPoly er et gratis lydbibliotek for Decent Sampler som inneholder lyder fra en [Dubreq Stylophone S-1](equipment/instruments/dubreq-stylophone-s-1/) med noen ekstra funksjoner.
content.en: StyloPoly is a free sample library for Decent Sampler featuring the [Dubreq Stylophone S-1](equipment/instruments/dubreq-stylophone-s-1/) with some added features.

title: 4-track Glockenspiel

content.no:
Klokkespill spilt inn på kassett og spilt av på halv hastighet og normal/original hastighet.
Biblioteket inkluderer også impulsresponser for to typer båndekko og to typer romklang.
content.en:
A glockenspiel recorded on to cassette tape and played back at half speed and normal/original speed. Playing back at half speed results in an octave lower pitch.
It also includes impulse responses for two tape delay/echo types and two room reverbs.
